  month =        jan # "~22 -- 24,",
  abstract =     "Depression is a common mental disorder. Appropriate
                 support from others can reduce the cognitive distortion
                 that can be caused by subsequent depressions. To
                 increase our understanding of this process, a
                 multi-agent model is presented in this paper in which
                 the positive and negative effects of social support and
                 its relation with cognitive thoughts are modelled.
