  abstract =     "Internet and web technology penetrates many aspects of
                 our daily life. Its importance as a medium for business
                 transactions will grow exponentially during the next
                 few years. In terms of the involved market volume, the
                 B2B area will hereby be the most interesting area.
                 Also, it will be the place, where the new technology
                 will lead to drastic changes in established customer
                 relationships and business models. In an era where open
                 and flexible electronic commerce provides new types of
                 services to its users, simple 1-1 connections will be
                 replaced by n-m relationships between customers and
                 vendors. This new flexibility in electronic trading
                 will generate serious challenges. The main problem
